multipleProfilesError.message:
The extension cannot automate the browser running with multiple user profiles.
Restart the browser and use a single profile at a time.

multipleWindowsError.message:
The extension was enabled but it cannot access the browser windows that were already open.
Restart the browser before trying to use the extension.

nativeHostDisconnected.message:
The native part of the extension is not configured correctly.
Re-install the extension from UiPath Studio.
